commitResults.messageBody:
Added new changes to the students' contact, in particular, users can
add new their students' student ID, module code and tutorial class.

Current version users must specify all the fields to add a new student.

Let's,
* Add 3 new classes, StudentId, ModuleCode and TutorialClass to support
the new fields in the 'Add' command.
* Update AddCommand and AddCommandParser to support the new format
* Update CliSyntax to support the new command tags.
* Update the UI to display the students information.
